# Sifu Pangda — GDD v1.0

## Character Overview
* **Race:** Panda
* **Role:** Tank, Initiator
* **Realm:** Gui Lin (GL)
* **HP:** 300
* **Level-up Rounds:** 0 / 4 / 6
* **Personality:** Meditating master. Calm, centered, unhurried — until provoked.
  *"Those who interrupt my XiuXing shall embrace the fiercest burn."*

